[SN]TITLE[SN]
African dream: The Ugandan women making fashion in Africa

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Definition Africa is a Ugandan fashion label founded by Nadia Bhegani, Olga Mugyenyi and Nahida Bhegani, which tries to source all of its raw materials on the continent.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
17 November 2014 Last updated at 17:53 GMT
This trio provides a tour of their company and explain the principles that have guided their business as part of the African Dream series.
